     <div type="epigrams">
   <head>IOANNIS FORBESII <hi>filij.</hi>
   </head>
   <div type="epigram">
      <head>Epigramma de scopo Authoris.</head>
      <lg>
         <l>FOrbesius, Româpompam iactante, dolebat</l>
         <l>Ʋno orbem obtundi nocte dieque sono:</l>
         <l>Ostenditque feram hoc signo ac Babylonanotari.</l>
         <l>Inunc, consensum maecha molesta crepa.</l>
      </lg>
   </div>
   <div type="epigram">
      <head>Eiusdem ad Zoilum.</head>
      <lg>
         <l>CAece, Theonino quid dente incognita mordes?</l>
         <l>Non tibi, sed doctis, Zoile, scriptalegis.</l>
      </lg>
   </div>
   <div type="epigram">
      <head>Eiusdem ad beneuolum lectorem.</head>
      <lg>
         <l>NEleuiter summam solum, bone lector, arenam</l>
         <l>Liba, neu <gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
               <desc>•</desc>
            </gap>icco rade profunda pede:</l>
         <l>Hic sulcanda via est, huic te duce numine oportet,</l>
         <l>Etpoteris placi<gap reason="illegible" resp="#apex" extent="1 letter">
               <desc>•</desc>
            </gap>ae credere tutus aquae.</l>
      </lg>
   </div>
</div>
